Class MultiPolygonGeoJSON

    Validation

    public class MultiPolygonGeoJSON
extends GeometryGeoJSON
    A Bean representation of a GeoJSON MultiPolygon geometry object. From the GeoJSON Specification version 1.0: For type "MultiPolygon", the "coordinates" member must be an array of Polygon coordinate arrays.
